      "representative_excerpt": "The Department correctly observes that the words that entities use to describe themselves can be misleading in some contexts. I support the Department\u2019s well-intended efforts to ensure that accrediting agencies appropriately represent themselves with respect to the geographic scope of the Department\u2019s recognition. The Department reasonably states that \u201cto th..."
