      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-09T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 429,
      "representative_excerpt": "On behalf of the Middle States Commission on Higher Education (MSCHE), the attached comment is being submitted in response to the United States Department of Education\u2019s notice regarding revision and clarification of its prior interpretation on the use of descriptive terms by Department-recognized accrediting agencies, specifically, the use of \u201cregional\u201d and..."
