      "representative_posted_date": "2026-03-11T04:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 400,
      "representative_excerpt": "Athletics is also affected by the regional accreditation stigma. The NCAA and NAIA ban competition from institutions that are not regionally accredited. <br/>That is monopolistic and blocks other institutions, that are accredited and have students that are receiving federal aid, from participation. <br/>I have attached the NCAA and NAIA rule below.<br/><br/>..."
