      "representative_posted_date": "2026-02-25T05:00:00Z",
      "representative_length": 218,
      "representative_excerpt": "As an administrator in higher education, I support this clarification. This rule change will protect students from predatory, unaccredited programs, as well as streamline the language used in accreditation discussions."
